 Gemini said
Ekta modern ebong professional Frontend Developer portfolio-r jonno nicher structure ba sitemap-ti follow korte paren. Eta emonvabe design kora jate hiring manager ba client khub druto apnar d दक्षता (skills) bujhte pare.

🚀 Portfolio Structure (Sitemap)
১. Hero Section (Introduction)
Ekhane apnar prothom impression toiri hobe.

Headline: Ekta catchy line (Jemon: "Building Scalable & User-Centric Web Applications").

Sub-headline: Apni ki niye kaj koren (Frontend Developer specializing in React, Tailwind CSS & JavaScript).

CTA (Call to Action): "View My Work" ebong "Download Resume" button.

২. Tech Stack (Skills)
Shudhu icon na diye, skills-gulo ke categorize korun:

Languages: JavaScript (ES6+), HTML5, CSS3.

Frameworks/Libraries: React.js, Vite, Next.js (optional).

Styling: Tailwind CSS (v4), DaisyUI, Responsive Design.

Tools: Git, GitHub, Firebase, Vercel, NPM.

৩. Featured Projects (Main Attraction)
Ekhane apnar shera ৩-৪ ti project thakbe. Prottekta card-e thakbe:

Project Image: Ekta porishkar screenshot.

Tech Tags: Jemon #React, #Tailwind, #Firebase.

Key Logic: "Built using React Router for seamless navigation" ba "Implemented State Management for real-time data updates."

Action Buttons: Live Demo ebong GitHub Repo.

৪. "Deep Dive" Section (Problem Solving)
Ei section-ti apnake onno developer-der theke alada korbe. Ekhane likhun:

Complex Task: Dhoren, apnar "Ticket System" project-e real-time status update kivabe handle korechhen.

Component Structure: Apni kivabe reusable components toiri koren (Atomic Design approach).

৫. About Me & Contact
Short Bio: Apnar coding journey ebong apni ki dhoroner environment-e kaj korte pochondo koren.

Contact Form: Ekta simple, clean contact form.

Links: LinkedIn, GitHub, ebong Email.

💡 Design Concept Ideas
Section	Styling Idea
Theme	Dark Mode default rakhte paren, jeta developer portfolio-te besh popular.
Animation	Framer Motion use kore scroll reveal ba hover effects dite paren.
Cards	Tailwind-er backdrop-blur ebong glassmorphism effect use korle modern dekhabe.
